### Footer Link Details

**Implementation:**
```tsx
<a
  href="https://travisjneuman.com"
  target="_blank"
  rel="noopener noreferrer"
  className="hover:text-accent-blue transition-colors underline decoration-dotted"
>
  Travis J. Neuman
</a>
```

**Features:**
- Opens in new tab (`target="_blank"`)
- Security: `noopener` prevents window.opener access, `noreferrer` doesn't send referrer
- Visual feedback: Dotted underline + blue hover color
- Smooth transition on hover

