### Lessons Learned

1. **Z-Index Planning:** Establish hierarchy early to prevent conflicts
2. **Positioning Awareness:** Fixed elements at same position will overlap - plan spacing
3. **Layer Categories:** Group z-index by purpose (content: 10-19, indicators: 20-29, actions: 30-49, modals: 50+)
4. **Security Best Practices:** Always use `rel="noopener noreferrer"` with `target="_blank"`

